title: Join us on December 10th for Common CAHSS
itunes:author: UW-Green Bay Psychology Department
itunes:summary: On December 10, 2019 the UW-Green Bay College of Arts, Humanities, and Social Sciences (CAHSS, pronounced "cause") will be hosting our first ever Common CAHSS Conference.  The year, the cause we're focusing on is human rights.  Learn more at www.uwgb.edu/common-cahss.
